              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401D1351-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>E fly from luxury and wealth,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-2" n="2">To hardships in pursuit of health;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-3" n="3">From gen'rous wines and costly fare,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-4" n="4">And dozing in an easy chair;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-5" n="5">Pursue the Goddess Health in vain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-6" n="6">To find her in a country scene,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-7" n="7">And ev'ry where her footsteps trace,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-8" n="8">And see her marks in ev'ry face;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-9" n="9">And still her favourites we meet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-10" n="10">Crouding the roads with naked feet.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-11" n="11">But oh! so faintly we pursue,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D1351-line-12" n="12">We ne'er can have her full in view.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
